name: Kalendome_B2
description: Kalendome is a visual exploration of the Kaleidoscope aesthetic, started in 2015, the project uses timelapse photography from different places in Brazil.  Kelendome_B2 is based on a timelapse sequence from Rio de Janeiro city, RJ-Brazil. Shot at the Sugarloaf mountain.  MP4 video, 2048x2048px, 13 seconds, designed for flat and dome screens(domemaster).
